com.interpss.se

Interface SELoad

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfLoad, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SELoadImpl

    public interface SELoad
extends AclfLoad
    A representation of the model object 'Load'. SE Load classs.

    The following features are supported:

    • PSe Rec
    • QSe Rec
    • Cur Se Rec
    • Shunt
    • Mva Base
    See Also:
    SEPackage.getSELoad()
